						<summary>

						<p>Two pieces of a broken slab lying on the on the river bank to the north-east of the village.</p>						

						<p>Beginning lost. Seems to be gift as <hi rend="italic">(utsava) mānya</hi> by a subordinate (name lost) for the welfare of the chiefs [A]mbadēva mahārāju and Jannayadēva Mahārāju. In characters of 13th century A.D.</p>						

